{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 29,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "iJpuSZDxZSBJHFSeavba",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "sister-m"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 149.118,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.601,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, there shall be many\u2014",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.781,
      "end": 7.75,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "at that day when I shall proceed to do a marvelous work among them,",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 7.93,
      "end": 10.624,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I may remember my covenants",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 10.804,
      "end": 13.451,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I have made unto the children of men,",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 13.631,
      "end": 26.541,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I may set my hand again the second time",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 26.721,
      "end": 30.668,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to recover my people, which are of the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 31.348,
      "end": 34.692,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also, that I may remember the promises",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 34.872,
      "end": 37.287,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I have made unto thee, Nephi,",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 37.467,
      "end": 39.65,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also unto thy father,",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 39.83,
      "end": 42.384,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I would remember your seed;",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 42.564,
      "end": 46.279,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that the words of your seed should proceed forth",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 46.459,
      "end": 49.153,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "out of my mouth unto your seed;",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 49.333,
      "end": 53.559,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my words shall hiss forth unto the ends of the earth,",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 53.739,
      "end": 56.107,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for a standard unto my people,",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 56.287,
      "end": 58.516,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are of the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 59.196,
      "end": 59.696,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And because my words shall hiss forth\u2014",
      "verse": "29:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 59.876,
      "end": 60.376,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many of the Gentiles shall say:",
      "verse": "29:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 60.556,
      "end": 61.056,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "A Bible! A Bible!",
      "verse": "29:3",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 61.236,
      "end": 61.736,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "We have got a Bible,",
      "verse": "29:3",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 61.916,
      "end": 62.416,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there cannot be any more Bible.",
      "verse": "29:3",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 63.096,
      "end": 63.596,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But thus saith the Lord God:",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 63.776,
      "end": 64.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O fools,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 64.456,
      "end": 64.956,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall have a Bible;",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 65.136,
      "end": 65.636,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it shall proceed forth from the Jews,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 65.816,
      "end": 66.316,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "mine ancient covenant people.",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 66.496,
      "end": 66.996,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And what thank they the Jews",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 67.176,
      "end": 67.676,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the Bible which they receive from them?",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 67.856,
      "end": 68.356,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, what do the Gentiles mean?",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 68.536,
      "end": 69.036,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do they remember the travails,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 69.216,
      "end": 69.716,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the labors,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 69.896,
      "end": 70.396,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the pains of the Jews,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 70.576,
      "end": 71.076,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their diligence unto me,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 71.256,
      "end": 71.756,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in bringing forth salvation unto the Gentiles?",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 72.436,
      "end": 72.936,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O ye Gentiles,",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 73.116,
      "end": 73.616,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "have ye remembered the Jews,",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 73.796,
      "end": 74.296,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "mine ancient covenant people?",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 74.476,
      "end": 74.976,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nay; but ye have cursed them,",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 75.156,
      "end": 75.656,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have hated them,",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 75.836,
      "end": 76.336,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have not sought to recover them.",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 76.516,
      "end": 77.016,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, I will return all these things upon your own heads;",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 77.196,
      "end": 77.696,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I the Lord have not forgotten my people.",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 78.376,
      "end": 78.876,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thou fool, that shall say:",
      "verse": "29:6",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 79.056,
      "end": 85.465,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "A Bible, we have got a Bible,",
      "verse": "29:6",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 85.645,
      "end": 87.688,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we need no more Bible.",
      "verse": "29:6",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 87.868,
      "end": 91.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Have ye obtained a Bible save it were by the Jews?",
      "verse": "29:6",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 91.752,
      "end": 94.817,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Know ye not that there are more nations than one?",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 94.997,
      "end": 96.622,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Know ye not that I,",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 96.802,
      "end": 97.302,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord your God,",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 97.482,
      "end": 97.982,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "have created all men,",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 98.162,
      "end": 98.662,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that I remember those who are upon the isles of the sea;",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 98.842,
      "end": 99.342,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that I rule in the heavens above",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 99.522,
      "end": 100.022,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in the earth beneath;",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 100.202,
      "end": 100.702,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I bring forth my word unto the children of men,",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 100.882,
      "end": 101.382,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even upon all the nations of the earth?",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 102.062,
      "end": 102.562,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore murmur ye,",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 102.742,
      "end": 103.242,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because that ye shall receive more of my word?",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 103.422,
      "end": 103.922,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Know ye not that the testimony of two nations",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 104.102,
      "end": 104.602,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "is a witness unto you that I am God,",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 104.782,
      "end": 105.282,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I remember one nation like unto another?",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 105.462,
      "end": 105.962,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I speak the same words",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 106.142,
      "end": 106.642,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto one nation like unto another.",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 106.822,
      "end": 107.322,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when the two nations shall run together",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 107.502,
      "end": 108.002,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the testimony of the two nations shall run together also.",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 108.682,
      "end": 109.182,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I do this that I may prove unto many",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 109.362,
      "end": 113.495,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I am the same yesterday, today, and forever;",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 113.675,
      "end": 114.175,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that I speak forth my words",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 114.355,
      "end": 114.855,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to mine own pleasure.",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 115.035,
      "end": 115.535,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And because that I have spoken one word",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 115.715,
      "end": 116.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye need not suppose that I cannot speak another;",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 116.395,
      "end": 116.895,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for my work is not yet finished;",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 117.075,
      "end": 117.575,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither shall it be until the end of man,",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 117.755,
      "end": 118.255,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither from that time henceforth and forever.",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 118.935,
      "end": 119.435,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, because that ye have a Bible",
      "verse": "29:10",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 119.615,
      "end": 120.115,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye need not suppose that it contains all my words;",
      "verse": "29:10",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 120.295,
      "end": 120.795,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither need ye suppose that I have not caused more to be written.",
      "verse": "29:10",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 121.475,
      "end": 121.975,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For I command all men,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 122.155,
      "end": 122.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both in the east and in the west,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 122.835,
      "end": 123.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in the north, and in the south,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 123.515,
      "end": 124.015,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in the islands of the sea,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 124.195,
      "end": 124.695,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall write the words which I speak unto them;",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 124.875,
      "end": 125.375,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for out of the books which shall be written",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 125.555,
      "end": 126.055,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will judge the world,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 126.235,
      "end": 126.735,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "every man according to their works,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 126.915,
      "end": 129.098,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to that which is written.",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 129.778,
      "end": 130.278,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, I shall speak unto the Jews",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 130.458,
      "end": 130.958,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall write it;",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 131.138,
      "end": 131.638,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I shall also speak unto the Nephites",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 131.818,
      "end": 132.318,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall write it;",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 132.498,
      "end": 132.998,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I shall also speak unto the other tribes of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 133.178,
      "end": 133.678,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I have led away,",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 133.858,
      "end": 134.358,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall write it;",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 134.538,
      "end": 135.038,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I shall also speak unto all nations of the earth",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 135.218,
      "end": 135.718,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall write it.",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 136.398,
      "end": 136.898,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it shall come to pass that the Jews shall have the words of the Nephites,",
      "verse": "29:13",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 137.078,
      "end": 137.578,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Nephites shall have the words of the Jews;",
      "verse": "29:13",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 137.758,
      "end": 138.258,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Nephites and the Jews shall have the words of the lost tribes of Israel;",
      "verse": "29:13",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 138.438,
      "end": 138.938,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the lost tribes of Israel shall have the words of the Nephites and the Jews.",
      "verse": "29:13",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 139.618,
      "end": 140.118,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it shall come to pass that my people,",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 140.298,
      "end": 142.341,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 142.521,
      "end": 143.021,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be gathered home",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 143.201,
      "end": 143.701,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the lands of their possessions;",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 143.881,
      "end": 144.381,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my word also shall be gathered in one.",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 144.561,
      "end": 145.061,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I will show unto them that fight against my word",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 145.241,
      "end": 145.741,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and against my people,",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 145.921,
      "end": 146.421,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who are of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 146.601,
      "end": 147.101,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I am God,",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 147.281,
      "end": 147.781,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that I covenanted with Abraham",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 147.961,
      "end": 148.461,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I would remember his seed forever.",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 109
    }
  ]
}